    "description": "Join our heroic and completely sane wizard as he travels the globe in his magic castle, on a quest to convert the world to gooey goodness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/a790970ff556747c4814f41e34eaa5a6.avif?t=1689575576\" width=616 height=218 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Game</strong></h2><br>A 2D puzzle game where the objective is to guide your goolems using a limited number of special abilties. Objectives range from gooing all humans, charging mysterious altars, and even capturing rare legendary beasts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Abilties</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dig</strong> - Up, down, left, right, whatever it takes to get round obstacles and suprise your new friends.<br></li><li><strong>Fly, Leap and Fling</strong> - Attack from above for that tactical edge.<br></li><li><strong>Spit</strong> - Gooey missiles infect water, put out fires, or make new friends from afar. <br></li><li><strong>Spit Wires &amp; Ninja Ropes</strong> - Swing, fly, or tiptoe across gooey tight ropes<br></li><li><strong>Sneak</strong> - Ground breaking stealth mechanics... Hiding in barrels.</li></ul><br>And more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/05a19c3a34ae92c1053ea0955072a16f.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/05a19c3a34ae92c1053ea0955072a16f.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/23b3519d685e62e6987c084e74580c6f.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/23b3519d685e62e6987c084e74580c6f.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/4d4f88b3227c83714f597d66ec94527c.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/4d4f88b3227c83714f597d66ec94527c.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/3b3f06a30d9cb6d34bfe8e737878284c.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/3b3f06a30d9cb6d34bfe8e737878284c.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/9404111de0686c0867c3217ce2ae0c26.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/9404111de0686c0867c3217ce2ae0c26.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/14ae23f7eaf0c813e58ac643f726ed69.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/14ae23f7eaf0c813e58ac643f726ed69.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/09364b98bd9392910dd368a43d24c36c.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/09364b98bd9392910dd368a43d24c36c.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/38be0ee4c754da114fed0bbdfa440375.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/38be0ee4c754da114fed0bbdfa440375.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/d333742f213028bbddc10bf33fb71d02.apng?t=1689575576\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/d333742f213028bbddc10bf33fb71d02.poster.avif?t=1689575576\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spread the Goo!</strong></h2><br>Dig the earth to let water flow. Goo the water to make... more goo?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/9cecf58e2afd20fe1620a94783d02ef8.avif?t=1689575576\" width=616 height=262 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crystals</strong>!</h2><br>Collect magic crystals to unlock mysterious secret game modes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166950/extras/a974759534a7f565088dea27b920b313.avif?t=1689575576\" width=616 height=270 /></span>",
